      @Contract(mutates="param3") public void getListing(@NotNull @NotNull String prefix, @NotNull @NotNull String spacing, @NotNull @NotNull List<String> current, @NotNull @NotNull List<String> exampleInput)
      List this node and any sub-virtuals to form a string-based graph representation in current.
      Parameters:
      prefix - prefix all substrings with this prefix, so it aligns with previous nodes.
      spacing - the space to append to the prefix for subsequent sub-virtuals
      current - the current graph
      exampleInput - an example input for NGram matching
